{
  "stem": "27390.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had to make the beds, like in the army, you know, straight, the blankets and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The blankets that we had, the one blanket, but it had to be nice and straight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was one boy with us, and he found out in the next barrack there was a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he managed to smuggle in a pair of tefillin to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he ran over every morning to this rabbi, just to put on the tefillin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very religious, this boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the time that when he ran over to-- to-- to put on this tefillin, we took it turns to make his bed because otherwise he wouldn't have had the time to make the bed and run over there, because we had to be out within 15, 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember the exact time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One morning we came-- one, one evening we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm telling you this episode because you asked me these questions about religion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One evening we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That means that the block fuhrer, the SS man, said the [GERMAN], room 18--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Step forward.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Step forward.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we all stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he went back with us into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked who sleeps on this bed?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This bed wasn't made.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The boy that was supposed to make his bed, he slept in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He somehow didn't make his bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he pointed to this bed and he asked who sleeps in this bed?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this boy stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, I sleep in this bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took us all out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was in the middle of the winter, in it must have been December or January, 1945, or December 1944.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
